    <item>
      <title>执法部门查获的假冒芬太尼药丸越来越常见</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/13/1250791924/fentanyl-opioid-counterfeit-pills-law-enforcement-seizures-study</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的研究称，去年执法部门查获的非法芬太尼中，几乎有一半是看起来像处方阿片类药物的药片。这一趋势表明非法芬太尼的供应量不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/13/1250791924/fentanyl-opioid-counterfeit-pills-law-enforcement-seizures-study</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>户外活动有利于孩子的视力。这就是为什么</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/13/1250555639/kids-eyesight-myopia-near-sighted-nearsightedness-outdoor-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[儿童近视在美国和世界各地正在迅速增长。研究人员表示，每天在户外呆两个小时的孩子患这种病的可能性较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/13/1250555639/kids-eyesight-myopia-near-sighted-nearsightedness-outdoor-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
